{
 "name": "RPlog_Shootout_on_Palanhi",
 "title": "Shootout on Palanhi",
 "summary": "Searching Palanhi City for missing companions, Alexis and Piper arrive at Starport Road to find a tense standoff: the Espo-escorted CSA man Dillon and a squad of Imperial stormtroopers facing off against the Wookiee Chewbacca and a band of fighters -- Khil, Jusre, Inoga, Leamer, Zarcane, Jander, and Miles Daq -- hidden behind the crates. The confrontation erupts into a vicious shootout, Chewbacca tearing into the troopers while the others trade blaster fire from cover and the stormtrooper CO, WA-1056, is steadily worn down. Caught in the crossfire, Dillon is badly hurt and dragged to safety by his Espos as troopers fall and the survivors rally medpacks around their wounded leader. The brawl leaves the squad battered and the rescuers scattered back across the square.",
